{"tid":584288,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"小林裕幸：《戰國BASARA》新作將於2018年公布","createTime":"2018-03-07T17:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T14:48:29.000Z","uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6be3f38c54f45c2a7e4d3c15b6a9fafcbacc6ff0","tid":584288,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"卡普空旗下PS3/PS4新作《戰國BASARA：真田幸村傳（Sengoku Basara: Sanada Yukimura-Den）》與大家見面已經有段時間了。很多玩家很想知道該系列什麼時候能有新作。<br />\n<br />\n在電擊PlayStation雜誌最新一期上，《戰國Basara》的製作人小林裕幸暗示將在2018年公布系列新作。<br />\n<br />\n當被問到系列未來的開發時，小林裕幸告訴雜誌記者，「2018年3月將會有新的戰國Basara舞台劇。由於我們正在做多個其他的準備，我會2018年時機成熟時做出公布。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/011747_963a871e3e7571f10fb89603722712b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F011747_963a871e3e7571f10fb89603722712b2.png&h=14448271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《戰國Basara》系列最新作是《戰國BASARA：真田幸村傳》，2016年8月25日發售，登陸了PS4和PS3。<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://read01.com/xDg2jgz.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FxDg2jgz.html&d=YlEOpzoS0lMG%2FjhymmpRW2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ded4b3f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/xDg2jgz.html</a>"},{"pid":"7bcd448ca72e472ea5c5be416ed53fa1a0eb6e5f","tid":584288,"uid":68916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"辣殺驚愈做愈柒,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ed259c5c184b6690aa2be45978f2becccc5989","tid":584288,"uid":55628,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7bcd448ca72e472ea5c5be416ed53fa1a0eb6e5f","tid":584288,"uid":68916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"辣殺驚愈做愈柒,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T23:57:25.000Z","msg":"再出烈傳系列 我就屌佢老母臭閪"},{"pid":"6c8c8d05f8f9fc97e38301d24d3f391c62f2f6d5"